Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:18.83,Pismo,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre, som v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:20.30,Pismo,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuji, pozri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:26.90,Pismo,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.14,Pismo,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:03.14,Pismo,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme? H-Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:05.63,Pismo,,0000,0000,0000,,Zadrž! Yuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:11.44,Pismo,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.19,Pismo,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuji!
